features: 🎮【All-In-One Switch Organizer】In addition to charging 6 Joycons, Kytok Switch storage tower is upgraded with powerful storage space, including 28 game cards, 2 Pro controllers and your favorite Switch OLED Dock. Featured with versatile design, extra storage for nintendo switch make your game area clean and tidy.

🎮【2H Fast Switch Charging Dock】Featured with touch ON-OFF button and rail charging slots, the switch charging dock storage charge 4 Joycons within 2 hrs. As long as the power supply above 5V / 1.5A can charge, Switch Joycon charger has various charging methods, including Switch or OLED console, wall adapter, HUB or PC. For LED indicator on charger for multiple joycons for the switch, Red means charging and green means charged or standby.

🎮【Powerful Switch Accessories Tower】With cartridge game card holder 28 slots (12 game cards + 16 game cases), 2 Switch Pro controllers and 1 Switch / Switch OLED console. When not playing games, Nintendo switch game case storage tower can also as switch console controller holder.

🎮【How to Install Joy-con Charger】 Firstly, confirm that all parts of Nintendo switch accessories storage are in place. Secondly, align the 4 brackets with the base then install storage stand for Switch OLED. Thirdly, install 1 charging plate and 2 controller hooks in Switch game storage. Finally, start to charge Joycons and store Switch accessories with Switch storage tower.

🎮【Exclusive-Design Switch tower】 Switch controller holder has a dock snap, not only to secure Switch Dock Station for easy grasping, but also more conveniently provide power for Switch controller charger to charge Joycons. Nintendo switch controller stand can accommodate all kinds of Switch stuff.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Installation Method Step 1 Confirm that all parts are included, including 1 base, 4 brackets, 2 hooks, 1 plate. Step 2 Take out the base and 4 brackets. Align the position and install the brackets on the base. Step 3 Take out the plate and the hooks (NOTE: The plate with the brand name "KYTOK" is placed above the storage position of the Switch console). Align the position and firmly press them into the stand. Step 4 Start to storage your switch gaming accessories.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks nice, works out great!
reviews.reviewText: Took about a minute to put together (probably actually less time.)The plastic feels quite sturdy and I am pleased with the ease of assembly! This fits perfectly on my entertainment center, and will allow me to display my game cases (and keep my games readily accessible) without needing to worry about taking up too much extra space! The only 2 (very minor) issues that I have with this product are: (a.) The rubber feet that are supposed to help it not slide around don't really do a whole lot - it feels like they just don't have any grip - and (b.) I'm not a massive fan of the way the rails feel when you slide your controllers in to charge them. Compared to other chargers, this definitely feels cheap, but it charges my controllers fine, so I won't knock off a star. Just being honest here!If you're thinking about purchasing this to help organize your switch accessories and games, go ahead and do it! It's a great buy!

reviews.reviewTitle: Alles in Einem - Perfekte Aufbewahrung und Ladestation für Switch!
reviews.reviewText: Ich bin absolut begeistert von der Kytok Switch Spiele Aufbewahrung mit Switch Controller Ladestation.Die Aufbewahrung bietet genügend Platz für all meine Switch Spiele, das TV-Dock, den Pro-Controller und weiteres Switch Zubehör.Alles ist ordentlich organisiert und leicht zugänglich, was das Wechseln zwischen verschiedenen Spielen zum Kinderspiel macht.Die integrierte Ladestation ist ein weiterer großer Pluspunkt. Sie kann sowohl die Switch/OLED Joycons als auch den Pro-Controller aufladen, was unglaublich praktisch ist.Ich muss mir keine Sorgen mehr machen, dass mir mitten im Spiel der Akku ausgeht.Das Design der Aufbewahrung ist modern und kompakt, sie passt perfekt in mein Wohnzimmer.Und die Qualität ist ausgezeichnet, man merkt, dass bei der Herstellung Wert auf Langlebigkeit gelegt wurde. Einfach zusammengesetzt - also kinderleicht.Ich kann die Kytok Switch Spiele Aufbewahrung mit Switch Controller Ladestation jedem Switch-Besitzer wärmstens empfehlen.Sie ist eine großartige Investition, die das Gaming-Erlebnis erheblich verbessert!
